<p><b>What is a communication skill?</b> Communication skills involve listening, speaking, observing and empathising. It is also helpful to understand the differences in how to communicate through face-to-face interactions, phone conversations and digital communications like email and social media.</p>
<p><b>What are the 4 types of communication PDF?</b> There are four main types of communication: verbal, non-verbal, written, and visual. Verbal communication relies on words, non-verbal uses no words or sounds, written uses written words, and visual displays information visually.</p>
